include ./includes/mixins

// CONTAINER FOR EMAIL
table(border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="table-layout: fixed;")
  tr
    td(align="center" bgcolor=purple)

      // EMAIL START
      // wrapper
      table(class="wrapper" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="600")
        tr
          td
            include ./includes/top-matter
            include ./includes/header

        include ./includes/banner

        tr
          td
            //- Add border to this table when we need it
            table(border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="table-layout: fixed;")
              tr
                td(class="padding-extra25-top" align="center" bgcolor=purple style="padding: 25px 0px 15px 0px;")
                  // wrapper 
                  table(class="wrapper" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="600")
                    tr
                      td
                        table(border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" align="center" class="wrapper")

                          tr
                            td(align="center" class="padding-no-bottom" style="padding: 10px 0px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ada0cc;")
                              table(border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="480" align="center" class="wrapper")
                                +kicker('A SPECIAL GIFT FOR YOU', veryLightPurple)

                                //- HEADLINE
                                tr
                                  td(class="body-text-headline" style="padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: #{ffMedium}; font-weight: 600; font-size: 42px; text-align: center; line-height: 50px; text-shadow: #{textShadow}; color: #{textColorReverse};") $50 off OMED &mdash; ONE DAY ONLY for A.T. Still
                                
                                +subhead('Hurry, you only have 24 hours to save big. Offer ends on Aug. 7.', veryLightPurple)

                                tr
                                  td(class="body-text" style="font-family: #{ffBook}; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; padding: 0px 0px 25px; font-weight: normal; text-align: left; color: #{textColorReverse};") 
                                    | Today, we celebrate a BIG event &mdash; the birthday of our founder, A.T. Still! Celebrate by taking advantage of our FLASH SALE SAVINGS &mdash; $50 off OMED registration.

                                tr
                                  td(class="body-text" style="font-family: #{ffBook}; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; padding: 0px 0px 25px; font-weight: normal; text-align: left; color: #{textColorReverse};") 
                                    | The festivities don’t end there. Continue the celebration at #[+grafLink('OMED', omedUrl, white)] Oct. 25-28 in Baltimore, where you’ll enjoy a stellar resident track, inspiring speakers, alumni events and a fun-filled Block Party. You don’t want to miss this premier event! Explore the #[+grafLink('updated conference program', programUrl, white)] to see everything we have in store for you.

                                tr
                                  td(class="body-text" style=grafStyleEmphWhite) Use code CAKE19 to save
                                    br
                                    | $50 off the current resident
                                    br
                                    | full registration rate.

                                +cta('Register Today', registrationUrl, red)

                                tr
                                  td(class="body-text" style=disclaimerStyleReverse) 
                                    | Promotion code is for residents and can only be used for the current full registration rate. Codes cannot be combined with other promotions or applied to one-day rate. Don’t delay, registration code expires on Aug. 7 Midnight EST.
                                    br

                                tr
                                  td(class="body-text" style=disclaimerStyleReverse) 
                                    | The official website for OMED registration and securing hotel reservations is #[a(class="body-text" href="#{omedUrl}" target="_blank" style="font-family: #{ffBook}; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px; padding: 5px 0px 25px; font-style: italic; font-weight: normal; text-align: left; color: #{veryLightPurple};") OMED]. Any other third-party websites or solicitors asking for your credit card information are fraudulent and should be reported to #[a(class="body-text" href="mailto:conventions@osteopathic.org" target="_blank" style="font-family: #{ffBook}; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px; padding: 5px 0px 25px; font-style: italic; font-weight: normal; text-align: left; color: #{veryLightPurple};") conventions@osteopathic.org] immediately.

        include ./includes/footer
